{"tid":1739843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時唔好再眷戀街頭抗爭 呢幾日要海量文宣","createTime":"2019-11-19T17:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T18:15:37.000Z","uid":225437,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"798b645d6c82ad3af227bcb0e45ba2d083e76bfb","tid":1739843,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:59:33.000Z","msg":"大家唔好俾憤怒埋沒理性<br />\n大家今次要正中政府下懷<br />\n全力做大量文宣做民意<br />\n呢幾日黎明行動可以改變方式<br />\n轉做暗地裡塞鐵 死火等等方向<br />\n呢次區選贏 政府就會讓步<br />\n因為區選以往係建制遙遙領先<br />\n贏區選先至落到共匪面<br />\n但假如政府寸步不讓<br />\n香港人就出師有名做「三罷」<br />\n甚至建立工會進行持續性罷工<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜前線死傷慘重<br />\n需要時間重整旗鼓部署日後行動<br />\n如果你呢刻仲係想屌狗<br />\n仲係想拎把遮就企前排<br />\n我只可以話你係會on99累街坊<br />\n和勇一齊喺呢個禮拜做好文宣<br />\n出現超過200萬選票投民主派區議員"},{"pid":"d8b7ef93c09182ce411e1e06ddd0ed382afdddfd","tid":1739843,"uid":304355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推"},{"pid":"92ae6609c4f708dd7f2e7817bbd2521a2665635a","tid":1739843,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:07:48.000Z","msg":"呢張做素材？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TE4Tpiz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTE4Tpiz.jpg&h=2fea4e04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cc08ca6f800eb11b625ba64111314e7a4861036","tid":1739843,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:08:41.000Z","msg":"泛民區議會選舉前快啲做野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737778</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推"},{"pid":"890dee98a3e002e16c2b7be6e011f554a1ca722f","tid":1739843,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:08:52.000Z","msg":"200個暴動<br />\n又快區選"},{"pid":"a6d02fe759f4471fcf649fca986f1252f03538d9","tid":1739843,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:09:49.000Z","msg":"